                </p>
                <button onclick="add('QR')">+ ADD</button>
            </div>
            <div class="product-block">
                <h3>RSVP</h3>
                <h4>50 tickets</h4>
                <p>
                    Service of contacting your guests throught phone calls or your favorite messaging app, including media messages as photo or video.
                </p>
                <button onclick="add('RSVP')">+ ADD</button>
            </div>
            <div class="product-block">
                <h3>STD</h3>
                <h4>50 tickets</h4>
                <p>
                    Service of sending Save the Dates messages throught your favorite messaging app, including media messages as photo or video.
                </p>
                <button onclick="add('STD')">+ ADD</button>
            </div>
